        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Eulima orthophyes Sturany, 1903, Locality 32 (Gul Mohammad, Saudi Arabia, Red Sea). A-E, G. Holotype, NHMW 37810: front (A-B), right side (C-D), back (E), protoconch (G). F. Original figure by Sturany (1903). H. Original holotype label. Scale bars: A-E: 1 mm, G: 0.1 mm." ;
